Module me.nort3x.quanta
Package me.nort3x.quanta.pub.basic

Class Deserializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.nort3x.quanta.pub.basic.Deserializer
  • public final class Deserializer
extends java.lang.Object

    Deserializer

    this class will `unpack` data from binary format please do not use this for conversions! unpacking is sequential meaning that you have to read the data in the same order you packed it
    See Also:
    Serializer, Converters
